        "title": "Dear Landlord",
        "body": "<p>I saw Dear Landlord on Monday night at Mac&rsquo;s Bar in East Lansing. I&rsquo;ve been listening to <a href=\"http://www.punknews.org/article/34112\">Dream Homes</a> regularly for the last year and the live show these guys put on did not disappoint. Tom Izzo&rsquo;s back and the entire town I think was ecstatic. I slightly remember driving by <a href=\"http://www.crunchyseastlansing.com/\">Crunchy&rsquo;s</a> on my way out of town.\n\n</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/joefearnley/4708436221/\" title=\"Dear Landlord at mac's by joefearnley, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4023/4708436221_7756fdc433.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" alt=\"Dear Landlord at mac's\"/></a>\n</div>\n\nIt was defintely one of the best shows I&rsquo;ve seen at Mac&rsquo;s. Although, I haven&rsquo;t really been to a bad one (the Gaslight Anthem show with thirty other people is ringing a bell) and <a href=\"http://www.myspace.com/offwiththeirheads\">Off With Their Heads</a> wasn&rsquo;t bad. Regardless, they have there, according to Jason, the best pinball game ever made. I don&rsquo;t know if I&rsquo;d personally go that far, but it sure was fun. \n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/joefearnley/4708460741/\" title=\"Medieval Madness by joefearnley, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4017/4708460741_947b66bf4c.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" alt=\"Medieval Madness\"/></a>\n</div>\n\nSometimes you can&rsquo;t control rock &lsquo;n roll. You let it control you.",
