        "body": "<p>Yes, that&rsquo;s right, I&rsquo;m bringing the Sunday social back. Let&rsquo;s start by having a quick review. </p>\n\n<p>One by one, I&rsquo;ve joined a gym and have been hitting it pretty heavy. No weight lost, but it feels good. It also feels good to be part of a &ldquo;private wellness club&rdquo;. Just a club to be honest. I can shower there and it even has a steam room and sauna. </p>\n\n<p>I&rsquo;ve been trying to learn Python. I&rsquo;ve on my way. I bought a <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Learning-Python-Second-Mark-Lutz/dp/0596002815\">book</a> and have been attempting <a href=\"http://www.pythonchallenge.com/\">the challenge</a>. Documented <a href=\"http://github.com/joefearnley/python-challenge\">here</a>.  </p>\n\n<p>I&rsquo;m also officially in two bands. One where we have recordings and one where we recorded three songs in a day. Life goes by fast. If you take minute, add some creativity, and try to make something happen, I guarantee you&rsquo;ll feel like a better person. And for those of you who didn&rsquo;t know I can play the guitar, here is a teaser for you - <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/#!/video/video.php?v=786136928252&amp;subj=12108490\">http://www.facebook.com/#!/video/video.php?v=786136928252&amp;subj=12108490</a></p>",
