        "title": "bring me the puke bucket",
        "body": "<p>As a follow up to my <a title=\"http://joef.org/2009/01/21/ap-et-match-made-somewhere/\" href=\"http://joef.org/2009/01/21/ap-et-match-made-somewhere/\">previous post</a>, I thought I would write about the next phase of the AP and ET relationship. Actually, I don&rsquo;t really care about the relationship, I just can&rsquo;t get over the latest ap podcast with <a title=\"http://www.bringmethehorizon.co.uk/\" href=\"http://www.bringmethehorizon.co.uk/\">this band</a>. These guys really do sound like a bunch of lazy, ignorant fucks. I just have a hard time getting my head around the fact that out of all the bands is seems that alternative press could interview, they go and get bands like this.</p>\n\n<p>Maybe I don&rsquo;t get the music business. Maybe I don&rsquo;t need to. Maybe I&rsquo;m just a fan of the wrong music. Maybe I should start my own podcast. Oh wait. Maybe I should start my own music-related podcast. I like this idea. I would probably be the worst interviewer in the world. Ahh, it&rsquo;d be fun, nonetheless.</p>",
