        "title": "sunday social #23 - why i autumn!",
        "body": "<p>Ahh the feelings of autumn and their regret. This time of year makes me a happy man. The change of leaf colors and the goodbye to summer. I have to say this summer was a pretty fun one. I saw some good shows and officially started a band. But that time is over and I look to the future for surprise.</p>\n\n<p>I have been doing a lot of work around my house lately. I learn with a lot on my where here with a little help from those I know. To be honest with you, I dont think I would ever treck down this road again. At least not without getting paid. My back hurts, my mind is frazzled, and I may have turned into an alcoholic. Jennifer Aniston has a <a title=\"jennifer\" href=\"http://www.freshnews.in/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/jennifer-aniston.jpg\">nice but</a>.</p>\n\n<p>I hooked up the cable in the basement and there is television in <a title=\"The Brown Out\" href=\"http://www.myspace.com/drinkthebrownout\">the brown out</a>. Still working on the keno game but my main focus for the next few months will be music. Fetch <a title=\"shoes\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/joefearnley/1818928479/\">my vans</a>, I job to do. Let focus on simple sentences.</p>",
