        "body": "Being the first day back from a long weekend, I thought the news would be a little slow. I supposed some of us could be excited <a title=\"http://www.google.com/chrome\" href=\"http://www.google.com/chrome\">google creating their own browser</a>, but I am little disheartened that we lost a great member of the entertainment community. <a title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_LaFontaine\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_LaFontaine\">Don Lafontaine</a> (aka Mr. Voice aka Thunder Throat) passed away yesterday apparently from complications from a collapsed lung. It appears this made his mark in Hollywood before getting into the voice over business.\n\nI found this on digg today. A good video. You will be missed. I can&rsquo;t help but wonder who will fill his shoes.\n\n<object width=\"425\" height=\"344\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/7QPMvj_xejg&amp;hl=en&amp;fs=1\"><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/7QPMvj_xejg&amp;hl=en&amp;fs=1\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"425\" height=\"344\"></embed></object>",
