        "title": "sunday social #14 - Jared S. Fogel",
        "body": "<p><img src=\"http://joef.org/wp-content/themes/couch/images/jared_fogel_2.jpg\" class=\"imbedded-image\" style=\"border: medium none \"/><br/>\nI happened to stumble across <a href=\"http://jaredremembered.com/\">this website</a> yesterday for reasons I don&rsquo;t remember. It appears that Jared the subway guy has passed on. According to <a href=\"http://jaredremembered.com/\">this website</a>, he died from &ldquo;<em>to abnormal abdominal adhesions resulting from his 1998 gastric bypass surgery</em>&rdquo; which surprises me actually. I was under the impression that he lost weight from walking to and eating sandwiches from subway. Wasn&rsquo;t that the the entire marketing idea they were selling us on? Seven grams of fat in a sandwich and shit. I am feeling a bit betrayed here. Its sad to see this guy go, but he made a living off eating sandwiches and talking about it. Basically being subway&rsquo;s bitch. I&rsquo;ve been doing the same thing for the last fifteen years of my life and I had to pay for them.</p>\n\n<p>Since we are on the topic of years of my life, I am turning twenty-six this wednesday. I don&rsquo;t have any big plans, but we&rsquo;ve tossed up the idea of going to <a href=\"http://www.yelp.com/biz/kumo-hibachi-and-sushi-portage\">the hibachi grill</a> or <a href=\"http://www.harveysonthemall.com/\">harveys</a>. Regardless I have a short work week with two basement shows to attend ending in a barbecue at my dads house on saturday. If anyone cares to join feel free to get a hold of me.</p>\n\n<p>This past week wasn&rsquo;t that interesting at all even with participating in quite a bit of nightlife action.  I did sing karaoke no two of nights. I really have to cool it with that. Its beginning to lose its appeal to me. Maybe I should just stop singing <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wo1npZWR5qk\">bruce springsteen songs</a>. I need a new challange.</p>",
