        "title": "sunday social #12",
        "body": "<p><img src=\"http://joef.org/wp-content/themes/couch/images/redwings_sm.jpg\" style=\"margin: 5px; float: right\"/><br/>\nThis week was full of mayhem and I don&rsquo;t really know where to begin. First of all, I had half of a tree fall down on my cable line in my front yard. It was pretty wild, but ultimately we got over it and met some new neighbors along the way. Nice guys, nice guys. They came over with the chainsaw and took care of business. If anyone wants some kinilin, let me know.</p>\n\n<p>On to event two. I went to the greek fest last night and got to see the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gin_Blossoms\">gin blossoms</a> play.  My mid-nighties rock dream finally came true. One of the first songs I ever learned on the guitar was hey jealousy. I gotta say it was really fun until the rain came. Then, in my punk rock prowess, I tried to get adam up to crowd surf and apparently you cant do that. So he was kicked out and I was toast for the remainder of the night. But hey, for being fifteen years in the past, the <a href=\"http://ginblossoms.com\">gin blossoms</a> made it fun.</p>\n\n<p>In my third venture, I have to say, some people just could be a lot nicer. I went to a vegan barbecue and apparently some people don&rsquo;t take liking to the fact that I think <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0109068/\" title=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0109068/\">airheads</a> is the best film ever made. Seriously, <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0108052/\" title=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0108052/\">schindler&rsquo;s list</a> was not that good and if you want to go apples to apples, let focus on the the eighties. I watched <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091790/\" title=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091790/\">pretty in pink</a> today and must admit that it might just trump both of them.</p>\n\n<p>And for my final awesome part of the week, I cut my hair. Well not exactly. The detroit red wings won the STANLEY CUP. Thats right, the wings took the steel city and it was totally awesome. I guess the shitty part about the whole thing was not hearing the  detroit fans in the crowd once was all said and done. When Nick Lindstrom picked up that cup and skated around with it, I was waiting for the roar of the crowd but it wasn&rsquo;t there. My theory was they would win in five which probably should have happened but what are you going to do? Wings win, I shave my face, and all is good in the fearnley house hold. My sister is turning thirty next week and I am having a party. The kegs will be flowing and the bar will be hooked up. Come on over. Once is all said and done, I wont remember a thing.</p>",
