        "title": "sunday social #6",
        "body": "<p><img src=\"http://joef.org/wp-content/themes/couch/images/gutter.jpg\" class=\"imbedded-image\"/><br/>\nTime ticks, teeth click and we don&rsquo;t have any chicks. Chicks? We don&rsquo;t have any chips!</p>\n\n<p>chips! chips!</p>\n\n<p>Sorry, thats a bad <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0110759/\" title=\"pcu\">movie reference</a> but a great way to start out a sunday social. The good thing about this week is that the weather is getting totally awesome here in west michigan but I&rsquo;m not getting too excited. It seems that it does this every year around this time and the april showers kick in. Then when the end of june rolls around the warm weather really hits, which brings me to my next conclusion.</p>\n\n<p>I seem to be gaining weight like those mountain tops  losing snow that al gore shows in <a href=\"http://www.climatecrisis.net/\" title=\"truth?\">his movies</a> . Slowly but surely. As the pureness of the earth&rsquo;s atmosphere fades, so does my slenderness. I guess I have it all to blame on the beer and bar food I eat. And when I mean bar food I mean only bars that serve pizza. There&rsquo;s something about that cheese and zesty sauce that draws me in. So this must be the time to kick it in to second gear and man up to the resolution I made this year. Plenty of push ups and lots of rope to be jumped. We&rsquo;ll see if I can do it the natural way. I have a plan to eat a lot of salads and drink a lot of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/St._Ides\" title=\"st. ides\">malt liquor</a> this spring and summer.</p>\n\n<p>In other news I got to try out the grill this weekend. We cooked ribs, chicken, burgers, and even&hellip;thats right&hellip;pizza. It was really hot when I tried to take it off of the grill though. Maybe I did something wrong but it tasted great and I <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/joefearnley/2429348451/\" title=\"broke\">broke the sink</a> in the process some how. And the red wings won. Round two! Off to texas for a good time and great barbecue.</p>\n\n<p>I watched some superb eighties movies this weekend. I saw <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0086927/\" title=\"bachelor party\">bachelor party</a>, <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0092718/\" title=\"cant buy me love\">cant buy me love</a>, <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0087985/\" title=\"red dawn\">red dawn</a> and <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0093780/\" title=\"principle\">the principle</a>. I also watched the nofx show on fuse a couple of times this week. I gotta say its quite amusing but I continue to struggle with the fact that they actually have a show on national television. Regardless, I&rsquo;ll keep watchin&rsquo; hoping that I really dont have to trump college chicks about sex in the city trivia again.</p>",
