        "body": "<p>Since this day only happens every four (or is it five?) years, I thought I would write about it. I see I am not the only one that was wondering this - why the hell are we working today? I mean come on current employer, we get good friday off and not leap day or martin luther king jr. day? What next? Jesus&rsquo; birthday? Racists.</p>\n\n<p>On top of even having to get up today, it seems that this snow will not stop. So if this god is really all omnipotent and shit, tell that cock sucker to bring on some sunshine. I getting really effing depressed down here. On top of that, as I am half way to work, the guy on the radio comes on to suggest giving yourself a little extra time to get to work today being that the roads are completely covered with a few inches of snow. Not shit buddy. Where were you 15 minutes ago when I was in the shower?</p>\n\n<p>I guess I can pray to st patty. Please dude, can bring some warm weather with you? I guess thats more of a question. Regardless, fuck winter, winter sucks.</p>\n\n<p>Joe</p>",
