        "title": "the other white meat",
        "body": "<p><img src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2049/2251917032_89e8f47104_o.jpg\" alt=\"spam\" style=\"margin: 5px; float: right\" height=\"117\" width=\"137\"/></p>\n\n<p>The other day, after checking the email account in which my comment posts and user submission get sent to , I have about three hundred emails in the box. Seeing as how  over the last 2+ years, only 3 people have left a comment and 4 people actually sent a user submission to me, I figured I got spammed. This happened once last summer on a post I created almost two years ago. It actually looked like a human wrote them, so I left them there out of amusement.</p>\n\n<p>But this was a different story. There were upwards of three hundred all wanting me to visit their <a href=\"http://del.icio.us/ViginaLinks\">del.icio.us list of vagina links</a> and sites full of free ring tones. The email address names were quite amusing as well. This is one of my favorites:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"mailto:buywellbutrin@aolin7.com\">buywellbutrin@aolin7.com</a></p>\n\n<p>And I added the mailto link so I can hope someone will spam them back.</p>\n\n<p>As a result of this I have removed my user submission and comment forms from the site. I am in the process of setting up <a href=\"http://wordpress.org\">wordpress</a> and they have a <a href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Akismet\">plugin</a> to handle problems like this. Until then, those who know how to contact me will.</p>\n\n<p>joe</p>",
