        "note_count": 0,
        "title": "something smells",
        "body": "<p>So I see today apple <a href=\"http://events.apple.com.edgesuite.net/f27853y2/event/index.html?internal=fj2l3s9dm\">unleashed</a> a couple of cool new things today. Like many I was expecting a new laptop, but not really <a href=\"http://www.apple.com/macbookair/\">this thing</a>. It seems the only thing about this guy that grabs me is the thinness of it. It just looks way to chinsy for my careless ass. I was hoping for a smaller version of the macbook pro. Same look, only smaller with a 12” wide screen. It’s appears to be the same size as the mac book, only thinner.  No optical drive, only one usb port, and no firewire drives me away. Looks like I will continue to proceed with <a href=\"http://www.apple.com/macbook/\">my previous decision.</a></p>\n\n<p>I do like the idea of <a href=\"http://www.apple.com/timecapsule/\">this time capsule thing</a>. I mean, theres nothing at all revolutionary about it, but if it works well with the macs on your network, thats a pretty good backup solution thats decently priced.</p>\n\n<p>In personal news, I dont really have much news at all. I am now a (semi) proud home owner, so I guess thats news. Between the holidays, getting things squared away with this house and being sick as a dog, I haven’t had any motivation but do much else but sit around and surf the web. I do have plans though. Even though I’m off to a slow start, this year I resoluted to hit the gym hard, blog more, and write more music. I am still in the process of re-vamping this site. Due to the the reasons mentioned above, I lag. I have really moved away from making it look cool and focused on the functionality and usability. Which involves a bit of hacking <a href=\"http://wordpress.org\">wordpress</a> by getting elbows deep in some <a href=\"http://www.php.net\">php</a> code.</p>\n\n<p>Soon have a new place to live, a new lab to set up, and <a href=\"http://www.apple.com/macbook/\">new hardware</a> to play with. If this isn’t enough motivation, I dont know what it is.</p>\n\n<p>Joe</p>",
