        "body": "<p>I finally got my new phone back last week…I guess this post is a bit late. I have plans to re-design my blog in the near future hear and decided on giving this micro-blogging service another go. I have given up on <a href=\"http://jaiku.com\">jaiku</a> as you can see from the widget on this site. I dont really know why. Probably because its friendless or maybe because google bought it. Maybe that’s a better thing?</p>\n\n<p>I am thinking I want to give <a href=\"http://twitter.com\">twitter</a> a go. It seems stable enough and with its mobile version at my fingers tips via this phone, I am going to be hitting this thing hard.  See you in social networking land.</p>\n\n<p>In other news, the recording process is impeading greatly due to equipment malfunctions and the house buying process. Once this holiday season is over maybe I can come full circle with it all.</p>\n\n<p>joe</p>",
