        "title": "the new(s)",
        "body": "<p>Damn, two months deep and no entry. I am totally slackin as far as the blog is concerned. Anyway, on to the now&hellip;I have moved, I am moved in, and I am not quite settled. None the less, I like where I live and feel a need for creativity as the months press on. I will be giving <a href=\"http://labs.joef.org\">the lab&rsquo;s website</a> an update soon, so stay tuned.</p>\n\n<p><strong>news one</strong> - I settled with the <a href=\"http://www.ehx.com/ehx2/Default.asp?f=%2FCatalog%2F01_New_Products%2F05_Metal_Muff&amp;q=f\">metal muff</a> for a distortion pedal. I also settled on a new amplifier. I bought a <a href=\"http://www.musiciansnews.com/guitars/11/roc_pro_1000_head.shtml\">fender roc pro</a> for under $200 dollars. Ultimately, its a great sounding amp that truly can create anything from tight dust to mud-filled flow. I have no idea how else to describe it, so I gave it a whirl.</p>\n\n<p>So, again, I now own I <a href=\"http://www.ehx.com/ehx2/Default.asp?f=%2FCatalog%2F01_New_Products%2F05_Metal_Muff&amp;q=f\">metal muff</a> distortion pedal. I haven&rsquo;t owned very many distortion pedals, but I must say, this one is pretty good to my ears. Yet, I don&rsquo;t really play metal music, so it can be a little over the top for me at times. Actually way over the top sometimes. Regardless, It&rsquo;s rather have too much that not enough.</p>\n\n<p><strong>news two - none more none more black</strong> - This doesn&rsquo;t come as a shock to me because I heard the rumor a long time ago. I guess it just comes as a disappointment. I never got to see them in action. I got into them over the last year and a half which isn&rsquo;t a lot of time to invest in a band but certainly enough to know how they make you feel. The upside that really has nothing to do this the none more black breakup is <a href=\"http://www.strungout.com\">Strung Out</a> (the best band on the planet) is in the studio <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uqdU4F8J2M0\">recording new sounds</a>.</p>\n\n<p><strong>News two dash a</strong> - I have not recorded any music yet. I have sharpened the two songs I write about and will record them soon. My ultimate goal is to create a band out of this whole thing. I have no official confirmation with anyone yet, but I think I have a drummer and guitar 2 on board. SO I guess this leaves a bass player that wants to be a part of the dopest side project ever.</p>\n\n<p><strong>news three</strong> - news years resolutions are going decent. I have managed to grow a beard, but my health kick has seen little action. I bought a jump rope and PLAN to use it. I am going to jump rope to the entire jungleland song. I figure I do this and the rest will come with less effort.</p>\n\n<p>happy black history month</p>\n\n<p>joe</p>",
